# {{ identity.name }} — Runbook

Operations playbook per l'agente basato su Agno + AgentOS.

## Avvio locale (sviluppo)

```bash
# 1. Crea .env (vedi .env.example)
cp .env.example .env
# compila i valori

# 2. Installa deps
pip install -r requirements.txt

# 3. Smoke test
pytest agent/tests/test_smoke.py -v

# 4. Avvia AgentOS (chat UI + sessions)
python -m agent.main
# → http://localhost:7777
```

## Avvio in Docker (deploy)

```bash
cd deploy/
docker compose up -d --build
docker compose logs -f agent
docker compose ps
```

## Operazioni comuni

### Bench modelli
```bash
python -m agent.tests.bench_models --role {{ models.roles.keys() | list | first }}
python -m agent.tests.bench_models --role all --save bench_results.json
```

{% if autonomy.write and autonomy.write != 'DENIED' %}### Vedere proposte pending (propose-and-confirm)
```bash
python -m agent.workflows.propose_confirm list
```

### Approvare/rifiutare una proposta
```bash
python -m agent.workflows.propose_confirm approve <proposal_id>
python -m agent.workflows.propose_confirm reject <proposal_id> --reason "..."
```
